
# |<------ Preferably using up to 50 chars ------>|<------------------->|
# <tag><group>: <subject> (Max 72 char)
# --------------------
# Examples:
#   research(master): Publish master's degree files 
#   update: Add a code example
# --------------------
# Tag can be:
#   research  (create a new research)
#   update    (update an existing research)
#   repo      (repository details; README.md)
#
# (Optional) Group is:
#   (post id) The name of any repository internal folder that 
#   contains a post, write the name between parentheses
#   Examples: (compiler), (graph), or others
# --------------------
# Remember to:
#   Capitalize the subject line
#   Use the imperative mood in the subject line
#   Do not end the subject line with a period
# --------------------